The paper discusses a tool for verifying deep neural networks, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The tool also involves retaining and reusing code snippets, which relates to software engineering (cs.SE). The verification of deep neural networks also has implications for security (cs.CR) and control systems (cs.SY).
